---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About PixMidas – Free Browser-Based Online Tools"
  description="PixMidas is a collection of free browser-based tools for images, PDFs, text and everyday digital tasks. No login, no upload, no cost."
  canonical="https://www.pixmidas.com/about/"
>
  <div class="page">
    <h1>About PixMidas</h1>

    <p class="lead">
      PixMidas is a growing collection of free online tools built to make everyday digital tasks faster, easier and less confusing.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        PixMidas offers lightweight browser-based tools for common tasks like compressing images, resizing photos, converting files, generating QR codes, counting words and comparing text. New tools are added regularly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Private by design</h2>
      <p>
        Whenever possible, PixMidas tools run directly inside your browser. This means many files are processed locally on your own device without being uploaded to any external server. Your content stays yours.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Simple tools that just work</h2>
      <p>
        No unnecessary accounts. No complicated software. No confusing steps. Just clean, fast tools for small digital problems that come up every day.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Always free</h2>
      <p>
        Every tool on PixMidas is free to use. No subscription, no payment, no hidden limits. We are supported by non-intrusive advertising.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Currently in beta</h2>
      <p>
        PixMidas is actively being developed. Some tools may still be improved or expanded over time. If you find a bug or have a suggestion, we would love to hear from you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Explore all tools</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 0 80px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,113,227,0.2);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page {
      padding: 20px 0 56px;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 17px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cta-row {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 14px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>